high_descs: Go to the round table
Pick up the knife
Go to the sink
Cut the apple in the sink
Go to the fridge
Place the knife in the fridge
Go to the sink
Take an apple slice
Go to the stove
Put the apple slice in the farther pot
Pick up the farther pot
Go to the fridge
Put the pot in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a pot with an apple slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the dining table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the table.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a left into the kitchen, then hang a right and head to the sink.
Cut the apple that is in the sink into slices.
Turn around, head to the fridge across the room.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn around, head to the sink across the room.
Pick up a slice of the apple from inside the sink.
Turn to the left, go forward to the stove that is on the right.
Put the apple in the pot that is on the back right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pot that contains the apple from the stove.
Turn to the right, go forward, then hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the pot inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a pot containing apple inside the fridge.

high_descs: turn to the right go forward towards the brown table
pick the knife from the table
turn to the right go forward go right towards the sink
slice an apple that is inside the sink
turn to the left go forward towards the refrigerator
put the knife inside the refrigerator
turn around to the left go forward towards the sink
pick up a piece of the apple from the sink
turn to the left towards the stove
put the piece of apple inside the pot that is on the stove
pick up the pot from the stove
turn around to the right go right towards the refrigerator
put the pot inside the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: put a slice of an apple inside a pot into a refrigerator
